column4: NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "F1BF39A141FE4ED4C39127A5DC095928", "I\'m Whamon. Usually I live in the sea.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "FB24206743DF50B6BC4306BCD273832E", "I don\'t have eyes, but I can feel most things.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "1B1B7CB8486809BAE233F4A3FBCC8EA1", "This is {Partner}, my partner and he is {DigimonName}.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "235DE5D54D42D00405AB1A987B557E59", "Will you listen to my story? There\'s a beach cave near here where I rest.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "9ABB4FBB41532B3A291D33A97FAC83A5", "But, some mean guys kicked me out and I lost my important treasure there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF094EAB49C57543509D73AC23272894]", "4AD76D3C4222A182961B8B8C9AAA047D", "Please kick them out. I want you to help me get the cave back.")
